{{stub}}


This book contains generate knowledge of '''Advanced Analog IC Design''', especially for the advanced user. The main part of this book is around CMOS.

It is intended that this can serve as a useful resource for analog IC designer and analog IC design students.

For reading and understanding this book, you should have a basic analog and digital electronics knowledge.

